*** Run Debug for the first phase or scripts in translators folder***
Just go to run and debug section on the left pannel or press (Ctrl+Shift+D)

From the drop down list choose the module that you want to debug and press F5

Don't forget to set the breakpoints in respective code beforehand.

There are four different module there for debugging.

- First phase, by which the whole phase is executed.
- other seperate scripts in the first phase.